title: 260: East-West Practice Report & Senior Bowl Preview
itunes:title: 260: East-West Practice Report & Senior Bowl Preview
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks take one more look at the AFC (00:55) & NFC (5:08) Championship games before they reveal the standouts at the East-West Shrine Bowl practices this week (10:36). The guys also preview the Senior Bowl by taking a look at the star quarterbacks set to attend (13:10).
